    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "sutton_body",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 380,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 220,
      "text": "Don't encode your cognition\nintuitions into the training method.\n\nGeneral methods — search +\nlearning — that scale with compute\neventually outperform hand-\nengineered priors.\n\nBuild meta-methods that find\ncomplexity from data.",
      "originalText": "Don't encode your cognition\nintuitions into the training method.\n\nGeneral methods — search +\nlearning — that scale with compute\neventually outperform hand-\nengineered priors.\n\nBuild meta-methods that find\ncomplexity from data.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
