    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "karpathy_body",
      "x": 1540,
      "y": 380,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 220,
      "text": "Don't anthropomorphize the\nresulting system. It is not a\nhuman mind.\n\nNo biological drives, no curiosity.\nBrilliant in one moment, bizarrely\ndumb in the next.\n\nPosture: empirical familiarity.\nLearn where it works, where it\nfails, build guardrails.",
      "originalText": "Don't anthropomorphize the\nresulting system. It is not a\nhuman mind.\n\nNo biological drives, no curiosity.\nBrilliant in one moment, bizarrely\ndumb in the next.\n\nPosture: empirical familiarity.\nLearn where it works, where it\nfails, build guardrails.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
